Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You lied? To let Seylum escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was your conclusion\Nwhen you guessed at what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Milord Slaine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is a firefight in the hangar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their assassination team?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, Milord.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Princess Asseylum!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will cover you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:00:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate the Terrans!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy attack! Enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perform emergency launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not safe, Milord.\NThere is a battle outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is one in here, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.11,0:01:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get us away from the battle zone\Nat maximum combat speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Princess Asseylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.59,0:01:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still no word from her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...manage to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inko, come pick me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am terribly sorry, Count Klancain.\NIt was not my wish to get you involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. This is part of my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I came here under orders\Nfrom His Majesty himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emperor Rayregalia had misgivings regarding\Nthe subjugation of the Earth system
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,after the death of the previous Count Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, he commanded me to both\Ninvestigate that and to ensure your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I must get in contact with Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is possible to make contact. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count Klancain, transmission from the moonbase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Klancain, where are you\Ntaking Princess Asseylum?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Lord Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am in the process of evacuating her\Nto protect her from harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moonbase is a fortified installation.\NThere is no safer location.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, a battle was in progress there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rest assured, the enemies within the base\Nhave already been eliminated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please return at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. I will not go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...watched birds on Earth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Highness....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earth was recovering,\Nand humanity and nature were coexisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was you who taught me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That humanity and nature...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Earth and Vers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}could prosper together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You are right.\NI did indeed say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have dispatched\Nthe Stygis Squadron to pursue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seize the ship at the first opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:04:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, Slaine.\NPlease, stop the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And make peace with Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let us discuss the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That sector is dangerous.\NPlease return immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Count Klancain, please turn back at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid I cannot comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must obey Princess Asseylum's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stealth to maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Milord.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The spaceship Hadriacus\Nhas vanished from our screens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Continue your search.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Milord.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We needn't worry about\Nany pursuers for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... what am I to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earth's military is trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Slaine has the backing\Nof the Orbital Knights, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must make contact with the crew\Nof the Deucalion somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is one knight\Nwho is on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The one who delivered the message\Nfrom Inaho Kaizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count Mazuurek.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time to demonstrate\Nmy loyalty to Princess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Landing Castle, lift off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clydesdale Leader to all units!\NTarget the enemies off the ship's starboard bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't let them get close to the Deucalion!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy formation closing in!\N3 o'clock! Angle of elevation, 60!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Increase AA cannon fire to starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Message from HQ!\NOrders to withdraw, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Withdraw?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they got their results.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Results, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The real operation that used us as bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Order all units back to base!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang 00, 11 closing in.\NThey're on a return course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Inko and Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're cleared to land.\NGet them aboard ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They fled when they saw that they\Nwere no match for us, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are they playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Count Troyard, the UFE is withdrawing.\NShall we pursue?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:07:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. All units, return to base.\NThey are to rearm for our next offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, summon the Landing Bases.\NAssign them to moonbase defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, Milord.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does that belong to my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Lemrina...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did my sister–
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Will I ever see her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is Lt. Kaizuka's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing life-threatening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What worries me is that the Analytical Engine\Nis putting a strain on his cranial nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told him not to, but look at how far\Nhe expanded its domain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's ceded part of his brain to the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn crazy kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must do something to put an end to this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will address all of the Orbital Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect,\Nthat alone may not suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From the very beginning, the Orbital Knights\Nhave desired to fight Earth and occupy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count Troyard has given them a pardon\Nto do just that in the form of a royal decree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He has unified them with guarantees
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of status in the new kingdom\Nand Aldnoah activation privileges.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Asseylum, it was his betrothal\Nto you that clinched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you simply call for an end to hostilities,\Nyou will only lose their trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as your younger sister is at his side,\Npretending to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Princess Asseylum.\NIt is good to see you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being so kind as to assist me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You give me too much credit, Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am relieved to be able to repay my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...to the Terran boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Inaho Kaizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've received reports that a part of\Nyour force went to the moonbase.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would you mind explaining why,\NCapt. Magbaredge?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was an on-the-spot call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose the princess now,\Nwe lose any chance at peace for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Slaine launch a war like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:10:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Slaine I knew was kind,\Nadored nature, and loved the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was not someone\Nwho would engage in pointless war...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he do this in spite of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Slaine has not changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know if his actions are right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But he has always cared deeply for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He has always wished for\Nwhat was best for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even if it jeopardized his position,\Nor even his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always... believing that you\Nwould awaken one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I suppose that is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What you say is right, Eddelrittuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you able to make contact with Vers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:11:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. However, His Majesty is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to stop at half measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count Klancain. I require your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall use the Hadriacus' audience chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish, Princess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attention, all forces.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Operation will commence\Nas planned at 1500 hours UTC.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Man your battle stations and stand by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Marito, you're going into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'd hoped to have\None last drink with you, Doc,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but never got the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're in a low-pressure environment.\NI don't want to drink myself sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that.\NThis won't be the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, when I get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this one of those "final showdown" situations?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe. If we finish 'em off, wouldn't it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever somebody dies in action,\NI guess that was the final showdown for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't jinx us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! We're all going to\Nmake it back in one piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milord Slaine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the UFE has begun to mass its forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This changes nothing.\NLaunch all forces and intercept the UFE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we will request the assistance\Nof the Orbital Knights who back us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Assistance, Milord?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will launch an all-out offensive\Nagainst the entire Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They will know how it feels\Nto have nowhere to go home to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Nao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did good today.\NTake it easy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to launch an all-out attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it almost time for the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think it!\NStay in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yuki. Something's come up\Nthat I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's that face that says\Nyou're going even if I say not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And there's that voice that says I'm going\Nto be stubborn, so you may as well give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. When you get back,\Nlet's have dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a death flag right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming back alive, you got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. You do the same, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Inaho. Feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the Sleipnir Final Showdown spec!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this payload a bit much, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Getting close enough to use this\Nin a space battle would be nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like things are going to get nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's not taking this seriously at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are boys always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho, you're in no condition to go into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let us handle it from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? Do you think you're some\Nhotshot ace? That you're special?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've never thought that about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it, Inaho!\NWhy are you acting like you don't see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:15:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you go out now,\Nyou might not make it back this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be another miracle like last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want... to go through that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be the only one taking it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Inko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this, the kindest thing to do\Nis say nothing and see him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to worry about ourselves right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to Inaho, our odds of survival\Nare probably lower, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get real! I'm an ace, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Inko. Calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NEveryone will make it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My left eye says so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master switch, on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuel cell batteries, heating.\NVoltage, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Activating pump.\NAccumulator pressure, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Force feedback checking program, start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ejection seat functional.\NIFF confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tactical data link, activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All systems green.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang 00, ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...it is I.\NIt is Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Asseylum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am weary...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How goes the subjugation of Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to you today\Nto ask a favor regarding that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to make peace with Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please give a direct order\Nto the Orbital Knights to cease fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That, I cannot do...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earth can never be forgiven...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do not let our assault falter...\NBring them under our dominion...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather... Why do you hate Earth so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Gillzeria?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What has become of my son?\NConquer the Earth at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Father passed away...\NDuring Heaven's Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Filthy Terrans, you killed my son...\NAnd even my granddaughter, Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is what the ancients called this world.\NWhat they called Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rejoice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For I have discovered\Na Martian superscience...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is called... Aldnoah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magnificent... Mankind will\Nmake even greater strides.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aldnoah is the technology we dreamed of...\NIt will make mankind happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is a great power.\NIt must not be misused.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nurture it with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:19:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that there?\NIs that you, Asseylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How you've grown...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Become a fine princess.\NAnd lead our people to happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Klancain. I ask you to put your rank\Nand all of your connections at my disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, gladly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your loyalty, Count Cruhteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Martian bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glory to Vers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell is that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slice them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My servants, wipe them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open a channel.\NI wish to address all Orbital Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Milord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An all-out battle has begun between the\Nmoonbase and the United Forces of Earth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My fellow knights who have gone down\Nto the Satellite Belt and to the surface.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Launch a concerted attack against the\NUFE in your respective locations!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Demonstrate our vast power\Nto the Terrans once again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And show the UFE\Nthat resistance is–{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hear me, Orbital Knights of Vers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Asseylum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:21:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am Asseylum Vers Allusia,\NPrincess Royal of the Vers Empire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The conflict began from a single spark,\Nand has grown into a massive war.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's being transmitted on all bands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A multitude of people had myriad\N hopes and dreams that were at odds,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}resulting in great tragedy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a sad thing indeed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This war has brought me great sorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel both shame and a deep regret over\Nour use of power that was not meant for us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...succeed the previous emperor,\NRayregalia Vers Rayvers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and name myself Empress of the Vers Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I also take Count Cruhteo,\Nmember of the Orbital Knights' 37 Clans,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to be my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We, the imperial family of the Vers Empire,\Nwish to make peace with Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:10.65,T1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prayer of the Skies
